These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, dahlia, iris, rose
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, hiking, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, jazz, soul
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
House: tower, palace, farmhouse, victorian
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
 3. the victorian house is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the palace house and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the palace house is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person who growsrose is the fan of electronic##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who growsdahlia##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Flower          | iris | dahlia    | daffodil      | rose  |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | writing    | camping       | hiking     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | soul       | funk          | electronic |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| House     | tower        | palace        | victorian    | farmhouse    |

